condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :1. Governance Accountability Action Plan (GAAP) | Description :Carry out, in a manner satisfactory to IDA, allactivities listed in the GAAP, as per the respective deadlines (see PAD, Annex 7) | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :2. Joint Project Steering Committee (JPSC) and Project Management Unit (PMU) | Description :Establish, no laterthan one month after Effective Date, and thereafter maintain the JPSC and PMU with mandate, terms of reference and resourcessatisfactory to IDA | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :3. Project Implementation Units (PIUs) | Description :Establish, no later than two months after Effective Date,and thereafter maintain, PIUs in each of the Implementing Agencies with mandate, terms of reference and resources satisfactory toIDA | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
Finance Agreement :4. Project Implementation Manual (PIM) | Description :Carry out the Project in accordance with the PIM |Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :5. Grants under Agricultural Innovation Fund (AIF) | Description :Provide grants following the requirements ofthe AIF Operational Guidelines and Procedures applicable for each AIF window and enter into agreements with Eligible Beneficiariesunder terms and conditions acceptable to IDA | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :6. Independent AIF performance assessment | Description :Employ an third party entity to carry out anindependent performance assessment of the AIF for consideration in the Mid-term Review | Due Date :30-Sep-2015

Finance Agreement :7. Safeguards compliance | Description :Carry out the project following the requirements of the EMF, SMF, PMPand any required Assessments and Plans prepared in accordance with the EMF and SMF | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :8. Monitoring and Impact Evaluation (M&IE) | Description :Employ, not later than 4 months after effectivedate,an independent third-party M&IE entity to carry out: stakeholder analysis; impact evaluation baseline, midline and endline;ICT-based project M&E and reporting system | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :9. Computerized Financial Management System | Description :Enhance the project’s system of accounting byoperating a computerized financial management system to facilitate financial information and consolidation; the software packageshould be acquired no later than 12 months after Effective Date | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
